{"tid":2104491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[非分化]我想問點解今屆所謂本土派好似無個識咁","createTime":"2020-07-12T04:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T15:47:15.000Z","uid":50088,"like":17,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a2cdf09c84d23922b8915b72b8b8c19e67c8c33a","tid":2104491,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:17:05.000Z","msg":"屋企兩老深黃半個半土派<br />\n接觸時事主要靠燒山+新聞<br />\n我自己本土派<br />\n接觸時事主要靠新聞+連登<br />\n但老實講我地三個都對區自己個本土派+超區既參選人同佢哋既政績0認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要係成個運動到而家都1年有多<br />\n好多新人好似雨後春筍咁出黎既情況下<br />\n我嘗試說服過自己佢哋係咪好似ira嘅新芬黨咁<br />\n所以未聽過<br />\n但無意冒犯我見到某d參選人嘅身型我真係唔信係企最前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然大家可以盡情笑鳩我孤陋寡聞<br />\n但問題係如果你想擴大基本盤下<br />\n各個本土派知名度咁低既情況下大家點會投佢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6aea99694e7292a77389b6dd7b4b56f5b7813d","tid":2104491,"uid":258258,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:20:19.000Z","msg":"其實。。。香港有邊個本土派出名？<br />\n當日遊B當選都係唔知佢邊個<br />\n講出黎小On 9 但選素人的確係跟立場選<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5098cb34df1623d60af7e0601e618f8d2c0bd994","tid":2104491,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:23:00.000Z","msg":"其實都係一個好重要既問題<br />\n本土派宣傳真係唔多夠<br />\n就算係同路人 都要搵方法俾人知道佢理念<br />\n知道佢係同路人<br />\n而家好似淨係靠網上(連登)口耳相傳咁<br />\n<br />\n要知道真係唔係個個都有心機睇選舉論壇<br />\n我有d朋友都係因為唔太識王百羽所以都係投返鄺仔/岑敖輝<br />\n就算連登仔都唔係個個都識佢<br />\n所以其實真係要諗諗辦法"},{"pid":"b89d7cfdc22ae4391a36578408bb6b1479a6aa06","tid":2104491,"uid":309553,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:23:21.000Z","msg":"魚革之前都冇乜人識天琦<br />\n<br />\n入到初選=提高知名度=多咗人識"},{"pid":"35527570956f9902d21d8624143de3ec7d902a35","tid":2104491,"uid":50088,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9c6aea99694e7292a77389b6dd7b4b56f5b7813d","tid":2104491,"uid":258258,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:20:19.000Z","msg":"其實。。。香港有邊個本土派出名？<br />\n當日遊B當選都係唔知佢邊個<br />\n講出黎小On 9 但選素人的確係跟立場選<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:24:26.000Z","msg":"問題係游b一開始係選區議會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n建立左知名度先選立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且問題係經過左呢一年嚟發生左咁多野<br />\n建立知名度既難度同之前係無得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我相信而家龍門老細落去選勝選會大好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c511e6622f104be87a08a154e95b260c708a6bb1","tid":2104491,"uid":66260,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:24:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d7dfcf9cd0062b8f32f03e80bc0df6220d154e7","tid":2104491,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"識果d走哂坐哂 一係返左泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0499b44225b415d9a1a24eb299cba08aa6968893","tid":2104491,"uid":156076,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:25:32.000Z","msg":"因為本土派資源遠遠比泛民少<br />\n人地有錢請打手係呢到叫人含黃碧雲都得<br />\n本土派而家真係無呢個本錢"},{"pid":"f02e6dbf83ada9fa8049698af7e0e8d70c03fc88","tid":2104491,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:25:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a64f1d9f80e045b416e7197a84d52d6af00e0d7e","tid":2104491,"uid":78768,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:25:57.000Z","msg":"因為好多都係區議員 你唔係個區係爭啲 不過我想問你想人哋有咩政積？"},{"pid":"3e1ecfe2b2c46c085c91cdc54b2db746a77cc4a1","tid":2104491,"uid":238210,"like":0,"dislike